          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1060439-relyn?shelf=2011-reread">2011-reread</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/1060439-relyn?shelf=2010-reread">2010-reread</a>
